            <p>Students participate at either their own grade level or one above it. For example, anyone in 7th grade or below may participate in the 8th grade events, but an 8th grader may not participate in the 7th grade events. Students may participate at different levels in different events. Students below 7th grade may participate in any event. It is highly recommended that every team has 8 people so that they fill all the contest spots, but it is not required. </p>
